author: Minyvonne Burke
title: 4-month-old daughter of New York City firefighter dies of coronavirus, family says
description: A New York City firefighter and his wife lost their 4-month-old daughter to the coronavirus, the family said.
content:
A New York City firefighter and his wife lost their 4-month-old daughter to the coronavirus, the family said.
Jay-Natalie La Santa died on Monday, nearly a month after she was rushed to the hospital with a fever.
"She was very feisty. She was a little Angel… [+2865 chars]
